'''Woolwarricca''' was a large expanse of prairies on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] where [[Kybuck/Legends|kybucks]] often roamed. [[Yoda's kybuck]] lived on Woolwarricca before it was given to Yoda and sent to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

